research.synthetics.inertial_dampeners.d: Unlocks the creation of a pair of cybernetic Inertial Dampeners that can be installed onto you, reducing the hazard of falling.
research.synthetics.artificial_capillari: Learn how to create Artificial Capillaries, fundamental for creating body parts.
research.synthetics.artificial_neurons.d: Learn how to create Artificial Neurons, fundamental for creating body parts.
research.synthetics.artificial_tissue.de: Learn how to create Artificial Capillaries, fundamental for creating body parts.
research.synthetics.organic_feet.desc: Learn how to replicate Organic Feet
research.synthetics.cybernetic_feet.desc: Learn how to combine organic feet with machine, to increase maximum complexity.
research.synthetics.heart_battery.desc: Learn how to create a Heart Battery, to store energy internally within yourself. Required for augments and abilities that need power
research.synthetics.solar_tissue.desc: Learn how to create a Tissue augment that can convert ambient solar energy to stored energy
research.synthetics.advanced_solar_tissu: Learn how to create a far more efficient version of regular Photovoltaic Skin
research.synthetics.stomach_augments.des: Learn how to create a Metabolic Generator, that converts excess nutrition from eaten food to energy.
research.synthetics.artificial_skin.desc: Learn how to replicate organic skin tissue, as well as create cybernetic tissue
research.synthetics.fluid_augments.desc: Learn how to create the Vision Clarifier and Integrated Respirator augments, improving underwater clarity and underwater breathing respectively.
research.synthetics.hand_wall_climb.desc: Learn how to create a device that can emit an adhesive substance from your hands, allowing you climb up walls.
research.synthetics.launch_boot.desc: Allows you to create the Spring Heel augment, granting you the ability to launch yourself in the direction you're looking
research.synthetics.internal_plating.des: Learn how to create an armour that can be installed internally onto the ribcage, increasing toughness and knockback resistance.
research.synthetics.integrated_exoskelet: Learn how to create an exoskeleton for your leg bone, increasing swim and walk speed significantly.
research.synthetics.organic_hands.desc: Learn how to replicate Organic Hands
research.synthetics.cybernetic_hands.des: Learn how to combine organic hands with machine, to increase maximum complexity.
research.synthetics.extended_grip.desc: Learn how to create a retractable hand extension, increasing block reach
